        <h2>Why Creators Love Us</h2>
        <p>We've built a platform that puts creators first.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">üí∞</div>
          <h3>Fair Compensation</h3>
          <p>Get paid what you're worth. Our campaigns offer competitive rates based on your reach and engagement.</p>
